{"tid":2227260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪我先係痴線嗰個","createTime":"2020-10-02T15:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T17:24:27.000Z","uid":230314,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f327eb53ada125deea50fe91618caf4b6b7495","tid":2227260,"uid":230314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"背景：啱啱交完學費 呢期手緊 仲籌緊旗找卡數<br />\n個Fd約我去join個$200嘅（非期間限定）活動<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個Fd：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：不如下個月先 我今個月真係無錢<br />\n<br />\n佢：咁我請你 或者你爭住先<br />\n<br />\n我一向唔鐘意比人請 或者爭人錢<br />\n呢刻慳左錢但欠人一個人情仲濕滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：唔鐘意爭人錢<br />\n<br />\n佢：咁平我請你啦<br />\n<br />\n頂唔順佢死磨爛磨 <br />\n應承左佢join個活動嘅初級版($160)我自己比錢<br />\n<br />\n然後佢：但$200嗰個少人啲 同埋多野玩啲喎<br />\n<br />\n我已經好大讓步 但佢得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：咁你想點<br />\n<br />\n佢：一齊去$200蚊嗰個好唔好<br />\n<br />\n我：我講咩你都係要去$200嗰個架啦，你想點咪點<br />\n<br />\n佢：Yeah<br />\n<br />\n都開門見山同你講我無錢呀等下個月出糧先啦<br />\n係要侷我去<br />\n個活動又唔撚係聽日就無左 等多個月都唔得嘅<br />\n到最後好明顯盲嘅都睇得出我發悔氣<br />\n佢咁都Yeah得出<br />\n係咪我見識太少所以先覺得佢咁樣係痴線"},{"pid":"093f15ad5453629899433a3d39f492a832d5da85","tid":2227260,"uid":6378,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"佢想你join同一個一齊玩<br />\n但你走去join個160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7144051c9c0d3b8f91a83d5a28be14e411db64","tid":2227260,"uid":8500,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"你係痴線果個"},{"pid":"2b71e0074975cd8337227b0632d685913bed8ef2","tid":2227260,"uid":230314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"093f15ad5453629899433a3d39f492a832d5da85","tid":2227260,"uid":63